data.description: Welcome to this lovely 4 BD/2BTH Colonial Home in Inwood. This home sits in a very convenient location which lies minutes from shopping, schools, and railroads. There are lovely Hardwood floors throughout. The Roof is 8 Years young. The heating was converted to gas in 2021. Also the water heater was installed in 2022. The first floor bathroom was renovated in 2020. The yard is well maintained and has plenty of space for entertaining.
